race.description: Falvey's Hotel Gatton F&M Maiden Plate
race.comment: FRENCH RIVIERA (2) closed off strongly last start, beaten 1L over 1350m at Ipswich when coming back from a spell. Improvement to come and the addition of blinkers is a positive sign. Lloyd will give her every chance from an inside barrier. STYLISH ANGEL (10) found more like her best beaten 2.7L is yet to break through in seven runs. Finished fifth at her last appearance over 1350m at Ipswich on November 13. Well placed and fitter again gets her chance to break the ice. SNUGG (8) wound up strongly at the end of 1200m at Kilcoy to finish a head from the winner. The extra journey looks a positive and she is one of the prime contenders. STROMBOLI DELIGHT (9) peaks off a heavily bet placing at Toowoomba. An outside barrier requires a clever ride.
